Monday – Friday 9am – 6pm
Location: Aljunied
Responsibilities:
Develop a clientele base by actively seeking out new sales opportunities;
Proactively access, identify clients’ needs, and propose suitable consultation and business solutions to meet clients’ requirements using Company’s products and services;
Planning and conducting physical sales presentations to prospective and current customers on a regular basis by giving professional demonstrations or presentations of the Company’s products and services.
Coordinate and communicate with all stakeholders (clients, suppliers, other departments, etc.) to ensure smooth operation and key clients’ needs are met.
Updating and maintaining customers’ account records, including contact names and numbers for future sales;
Provide excellent customer service to existing customers to improve the quality of business relationships with clients and vendors;
